From: Performance Patch Series
Subject: [PATCH 10/16] 10-reduce-metadata-memory

True streaming GetObjects: yields one RecordBatch per catalog via
ChunkedGetObjectsStream, allowing GC of previous catalog data before
building the next. Replaces ineffective GC.Collect batching (Bug #9).
Extracts GetMatchingCatalogIds helper for catalog listing with retry.
Adds MetadataBatchSize parameter constant.

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>

